{
  "stem": "19195.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he says, we cannot give you, because she wants you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And you'll-- you'll fit in just fine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went along.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But as the days passed, and I missed my parents-- I was never away from them so far-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And by the time I came to the orphanage, I was knocked out, because I didn't sleep for days and nights.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I found a friend there that I didn't see for about four years.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were friends at-- at home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Raisy.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Hungarian, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "R-O-N-A or R-O-N-O.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Street, 52nd Street.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were very, you know, shocked to meet one another after so many years.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she sounded so glad that we are together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We grew up together, and now we're still friends.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said I'm very happy to-- to have found you, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At least I'll feel close that I have somebody that I know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I liked my job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I decided to stay there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were two children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh-- Oh, let me go back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Can I?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was actually not a real orphanage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was when they start taking the Slovakian Jews and the-- and the Czech Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 15 SECONDS] And the people would run away with the children, the parents.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this orphanage was known to take care only of people who left their houses, their homes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were active kids.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We-- we-- there was a little-- there was a [INAUDIBLE] that orphanage.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the kids didn't go to school, because we had teachers there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they really took care of those children.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
